Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:01.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種粒子光束是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.48,0:00:05.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.58,0:00:08.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.49,0:00:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  目標捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.16,0:00:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三部Gundam Throne判定為輔助紛爭的對象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.43,0:00:17.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.52,0:00:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  驅逐目標
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.68,0:00:29.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  搞什麼鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.24,0:00:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.37,0:00:36.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們幾個  那種機體…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.15,0:00:38.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能算是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.03,0:00:41.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:21.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.41,0:02:22.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦啊  約翰哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能聽到嗎  Exia的機師
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.67,0:02:28.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要妨礙我們行動
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:30.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是為了根除戰爭…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.01,0:02:31.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.50,0:02:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.17,0:02:38.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瘋了嗎  Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.70,0:02:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.97,0:02:47.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fang！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.41,0:02:58.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.89,0:03:03.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:04.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.21,0:03:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.26,0:03:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞·埃德…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.20,0:03:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Virtue  摧毀目標
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia在和Throne戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.76,0:03:19.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才Virtue好像也加入了其中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連特瑞亞也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然Gundam之間相互廝殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好會兩敗俱傷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.53,0:03:28.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也好啊  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.69,0:03:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三位一體的做法讓人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.05,0:03:35.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是個不錯的男的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.70,0:03:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  他們的行動也可能是計劃的一部分…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們採取的這種行動或許也在計劃之中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.35,0:03:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.76,0:03:48.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩·斯托拉托斯發來了緊急密碼訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.94,0:03:50.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在待命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:54.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓他盡可能阻止戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.80,0:03:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  根據現場情況  以自己的判斷為主
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:03:59.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就等於是隨便嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有失戰術預報員的臉面哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是這樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.16,0:04:11.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿里路亞你呢  要出擊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.44,0:04:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在這裡保護普特利麥奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此  這裡也並不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.32,0:04:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然心裡很想出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.07,0:04:27.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是會亂來啊  那個淘氣包
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.52,0:04:29.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  沒能阻止  沒能阻止
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅  你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.94,0:04:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  多虧如此  皇小姐也沉下氣來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  我也能理解刹那的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.12,0:04:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是想成為Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:46.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為實現根除紛爭的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.02,0:04:50.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說  我很想幹一場
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊了  哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.88,0:04:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dynames  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯  出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:03.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  Exia向新型的Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.76,0:05:05.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼做好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.21,0:05:07.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  會如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.13,0:05:10.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅龍  對我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.88,0:05:13.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這世界能改變就行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.95,0:05:16.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是採取何種手段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.26,0:05:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam之間的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.45,0:05:23.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比預想得還早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.28,0:05:26.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轉到第三階段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.43,0:05:29.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法挽回了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.59,0:05:37.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,採用S32陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.34,0:05:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN Field嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.15,0:05:51.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.53,0:06:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真沒想到還會和你搭檔使用陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:06.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.26,0:06:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia  Virtue  還在繼續和Throne戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:13.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像還採用了戰術陣型
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:17.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,S32  D07  甚至還使用了F52
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:19.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特瑞亞和刹那嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.28,0:06:24.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜  對接
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.76,0:06:25.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.51,0:06:33.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們以為  我會給你們留下這種時間嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.03,0:06:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以這種機動性的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.98,0:06:37.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事  機體的輸出功率…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:04.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,System down？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:22.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.53,0:07:29.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓與吠陀進行資料連接的機體全部被制抑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.23,0:07:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是Gundam Nadleeh的真正實力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅賜予了特瑞亞·埃德的Gundam Meister的試驗系統
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥  妮娜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.80,0:07:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們並不適合當Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.01,0:07:51.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們罪該萬死！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:07:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.80,0:08:04.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試驗系統被強制解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.56,0:08:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:11.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7區域內的部分資料被竄改了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.34,0:08:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個資料區域到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.21,0:08:17.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:20.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然連我也無法訪問
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.90,0:08:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然吠陀…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.50,0:08:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.94,0:08:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Dynames嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.98,0:08:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來就是三對三了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.92,0:08:35.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩組隊戰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就玩玩看！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:39.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邁克爾  妮娜  撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.74,0:08:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用這樣吧  老哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.66,0:08:42.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:46.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果Gundam彼此之間爭鬥  那會妨礙計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.57,0:08:48.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切  知道…啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.34,0:08:56.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.70,0:08:59.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我們來  你有更需要去戰鬥的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.10,0:09:02.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對嗎  洛克恩·斯托拉托斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  應該說是尼爾·迪蘭地
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尼爾·迪蘭地？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.84,0:09:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙  居然看了我的資料
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過吠陀拜讀了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Level 7的情報…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.61,0:09:21.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛克恩  你成為Gundam Meister以來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.43,0:09:25.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要復仇的人之一  就在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.76,0:09:30.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克魯吉斯共和國反政府武裝遊擊隊KPSA
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.65,0:09:35.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭·伊布拉希姆  乃是其成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:37.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  那是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.05,0:09:42.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索蘭·伊布拉希姆  代號刹那·F·清榮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.90,0:09:45.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說是刹那？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.70,0:09:50.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  他是殺害你父母和妹妹的組織中的成員之一
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的仇敵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.28,0:10:16.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7台Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.80,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總統…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.63,0:10:21.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經束手無策了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.62,0:10:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果胡亂出兵而拖垮軍隊的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我方陣營的經濟就會崩潰
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.92,0:10:32.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  就只能接受他們的要求  解除武裝了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:33.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別胡說八道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這麼做的話  那各國將會面臨名譽掃地
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:40.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:42.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.47,0:10:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲稱是Celestial Being相關人員的人通過網路和我們接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:52.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.68,0:10:55.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組織的相關資料也傳了一些過來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:57.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是事實
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.08,0:11:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此  是內部分裂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.75,0:11:06.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來神還沒有捨棄我們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在受到攻擊的愛麗絲公司工廠一帶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大量死者家屬聚集在一起進行哀悼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.09,0:11:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動攻擊的三台MS被證實是新型Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.05,0:11:23.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對此過激行為…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:22.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.11,0:11:40.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲  花
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.10,0:11:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:02.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈  你回日本去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.82,0:12:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休學可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.04,0:12:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然你能來陪我我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.42,0:12:11.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  你不能一直待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.12,0:12:14.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我把你孤伶伶留在這裡  這種事我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈你的夢想是去宇宙工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.67,0:12:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能因為我而破壞你的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.65,0:12:24.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.38,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使現在在一起  以後也會很難過的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直感到自卑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.13,0:12:34.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈會一直後悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.81,0:12:35.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.62,0:12:41.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  能把我的夢想託付給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.12,0:12:42.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:47.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實現夢想  這就是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.69,0:12:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以  去實現我的夢想吧  沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.93,0:12:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.18,0:12:59.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣約定了
