Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:12.88,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}As life goes on...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:18.32,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}忘れちゃいけないからYeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:23.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}Don't let it go...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:30.87,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}この広い大地の仲間たちのこと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:18.19,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}曾有著相同的笑臉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.46,0:22:25.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}就是那樣的我們也已過了多年
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.71,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}那交錯的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.96,0:22:33.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}無法接受並急躁著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:41.14,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}捨棄了無用的自尊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.46,0:22:46.83,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}給予這世界以溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.97,0:22:48.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}我要說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.20,0:22:53.40,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}即便顯示出勇氣　即便逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:58.11,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}一個人亦是無法生存的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.66,0:23:02.44,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}若是那天的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.75,0:23:07.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}依然存留在心靈深處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:12.88,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}如同生命的延續...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:18.32,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}由於不可忘記　Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.56,0:23:23.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}所以不要離去...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:30.87,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,250)}還要留在這廣闊大地同伴們的身邊
